data.description: Welcome to this spacious 4-bedroom 2.5 bath home located in the beautiful city of Surprise! Home features recently updated flooring throughout the whole home. Sitting right on corner lot accompanied by play pool with a built-in spa and water features. Come see it today! Seller financing available!
